## 图6: 整体经济闭环

```mermaid
---
title: SUIBOX 经济闭环
---
flowchart LR
    subgraph External["外部"]
        SUI[SUI生态<br/>资金流入]
    end

    SUI --> NFT[传奇NFT销售]
    NFT --> LP["LP流动性<br/>建立"]

    NFT --> Nft[获得NFT]
    Nft --> Box[获得BOX]

    Box --> Stake[质押挖矿]
    Stake --> Up[升级消耗]

    Up --> |"55%销毁"| Burn[BOX销毁]
    Up --> |"45%回流"| Pool[奖励池]

    Pool --> Stake
    Pool --> Invite["邀请激励"]
    Pool --> Comm["社区基金"]

    Invite --> NewUser[新用户]
    NewUser --> NFT

    Burn --> Price[BOX价格上涨]
    Stake --> Price

    style SUI fill:#87CEEB
    style NFT fill:#FFD700
    style LP fill:#90EE90
    style Burn fill:#FF6B6B
    style Price fill:#FF1493
```

