## 图7: 流通量控制

```mermaid
---
title: 流通量控制机制
---
flowchart TB
    subgraph Input["每日释放"]
        Daily["约13.7万 BOX"]
    end

    Daily --> Lock["质押锁仓<br/>50%+"]
    Daily --> Burn["升级销毁<br/>55%"]
    Daily --> Fee["交易手续费"]

    Lock --> Cir["实际流通量"]
    Burn --> Cir
    Fee --> Cir

    Cir --> |"供 < 需"| Price["价格上涨"]

    Price --> Attract["吸引更多用户"]
    Attract --> Daily

    style Daily fill:#87CEEB
    style Lock fill:#90EE90
    style Burn fill:#FF6B6B
    style Cir fill:#FFD700
    style Price fill:#FF1493
```

